_____________________
Dua in Roman English

Khudaawanda ! Karaar De Mujko Is Mahine Me Istegfaar Karnewaalon Mese, Aur Karaar De Mujko Isme Apne Nek Bandon Mese, Jo Tujse Lav Lagaaye Huve Hai Aur Karaar De Mujko Isme Apne Mokarrab Dosto Mese Apni Maherbaani Se. Ay Rahem Karnewaalon Me Sabse Zyaada Rahim.""",
    "translation":
    """O Allah, on this day, place me among those who seek forgiveness. Place me among Your righteous and obedient servants, and place me among Your close friends, by Your kindness, O the most Merciful.""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahummaj Alni Fihe Menal Mustagfereena Waja'alnee Fihe Min Abaadekas Saaleheenal Kaaneteena Waja'alnee Fihe Min Awleyaa'akal Mokarrabeena Be Raa'afateka Ya Arhamar Raahemeen.""",
  },

//dua no.6
  {
