    "audioUrl":
    "http://docs.google.com/uc?export=open&id=1dJsh9QIzoDHQ78om9vsuqBMsvJqMWXIk",
    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ لا تَخْذُلْني فيهِ لِتَعَرُّضِ مَعْصِيَتِكَ، وَلاتَضْرِبْني بِسِياطِ نَقِمَتِكَ، وَزَحْزِحْني فيهِ مِنْ مُوجِباتِ سَخَطِكَ، بِمَنِّكَ وَاَياديكَ يا مُنْتَهى رَغْبَةِ الرّاغِبينَ 
_____________________
Dua in Roman English

Khudaawanda ! Mujko Aazaad Na Chhod De Is Mahine Me Apni Naa Farmaani Karnewaale Honeki Wajah Se, Aur Na Lagaa Muje Apni Naaraazgi Ke Kode, Aur Na Door Kar Mujko Isme Apni Naaraazgi Ke Asbaab Se Apne Ahsaan Aur Ne'amaton Se, Ay Aakhri Nukta Ragbat Karne Waalon Ki Ragbat Ka.""",
    "translation":
    """O Allah, on this day, do not abase myself by incurring  Your disobedience , and do not strike me with the whip of Your punishment , keep me away from the causes of Your anger, by Your kindness and Your power, O the ultimate of those who desire.""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahumma La Takhzulnee Fihe Le Ta'arroze Maa'asiyateka Wala Tazreebnee Be Seyaate Nakemateka Wazah Zeehni Fihe Mim'mujebaate Sakhteka Be Manneka Wa Ayaadeeka Ya Muntaha Ragbateer Raagebeen.""",
  },

