_____________________
Dua in Roman English

Khudaawanda ! Madad Kar Meri Is Mahine Ke Roze Aur Namaaz Par Aur Bacha Mujko Isme Lagzishon Aur Gunaahon Se Aur Mujko Apne Zikraki Taufiq Hamesha. Ay Gumraahon Ki Hidaayat Karnewale.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Help me in it to fast and to pray as it is worth, help me avoid its slips and sins, and grant me in it to continuously remember You with Your enabling, O One Who guides those who stray!""",
    "transliteration":
    """ALLAAHUMMA A-I'NNEE FEEHE A'LAA SEYAAMEHI WA QEYAAMEHI WA JANNIBNEE FEEHE MIN HAFAWAATEHI WA AASAAMEHI WAR-ZUQNEE FEEHE ZIKRAKA BEDAWAAMEHI BE-TAWFEEQEKA YAA HAADEYAL MOZILLEENA.""",
  },

//dua no.8
