    "arabic":
    """اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِيْ فِيْهِ رَحْمَةَ الْاَيْتَامِ، وَاِطْعَامَ الطَّعَامِ، وَاِفْشَاۤءَ السَّلَامِ، وَصُحْبَةَ الْكِرَامِ، بِطَوْلِكَ يَا مَلْجَاَ الْاٰمِلِيْنَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Ataakar Mujko Is Mahineme Yateemo Par Jazbaa Rahemka Aur Khaana Khilaane Ka Aur Sulha Pasandi Ke Izhaar Ka Aur Kameene Logon Se Bachne Aur Buzurgo Ki Sohbat Me Bethne Ka Apni Bakhsheesh Se. Ay Ummidwaro Ki Ummid Ki Jagah.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Grant me in it mercy due to orphans, to be able to give away food, to disseminate the peace, to accompany the good ones through Your own favors, O haven of the hopeful!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahummar Zukni Fihe Rahmatal Aytaame Wa It'aamateet Ta'aame Wa Ifshaa'as Salaame Wa Sohbal Qeraame Betawleka Ya Malja'al Aameleen.""",
  },

//dua no.9
  {
