_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Karaar De Mere Liye Is Mahine Me Apni Wasi'a (Zyaada) Rahemat Se Hissa, Aur Hidaayat Kar Mujko Isme Apne Roshan Dalla'el Ki Taraf, Aur Leja Mujko Apni Razaamandi Ki Taraf Jo Teri Mohabbat Ka Sarmaaya Hai. Ay Mustaako Ke Ummid Ka Markaz(Jagah).""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Allot for me in it a portion of Your spacious mercy, guide me in it to Your glittering proofs, take my forelock to whatever achieves Your collective Pleasure through Your love, O hope of the eager ones!""",
    "transliteration":
    """ALLAAHUMMAJ A'L LEE FEEHE NASEEBAN MIN RAHMATEKAL WAASE-A'TE WAHDENEE FEEHE LE-BARAAHEENEKAS SAA-TE-A'TE WA KHUZ BE-NAASEYATEE ELAA MARZAATEKAL JAA-ME-A'TE BE-MAHABBATEKA YAA AMALAL MUSHTAAQEENA.""",
  },

