    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ حَبِّبْ اِلَيَّ فيهِ الإحسان، وَكَرِّهْ اِلَيَّ فيهِ الْفُسُوقَ وَالْعِصْيانَ، وَحَرِّمْ عَلَيَّ فيهِ السَّخَطَ وَالنّيرانَ بِعَوْنِكَ يا غِياثَ الْمُسْتَغيثينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Mehboob Karaar De Mere Liye Is Mahineme Ahsaanko Aur Nagawaar Karaar De Mere Liye Isme Fisko Fojur Aur Gunaah Ko, Aur Haraam Karde Mere Oopar Isme Apni Naaraazgi Aur Aatishe Jahannum Ko Apni Imdaad Se. Ay Fareeyaadiyo Ke Fareeyaad Ras.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Make me in it love benevolence, hate immorality and rebellion, and prohibit in it anger against me and the Fires with Your assistance, O One Who brings relief to those who plead for it!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahumma Hab'beeb Alaiyya Fiheel Ahsaana Wa Kar'reeh Alaiyya Fiheel Fosooka Wal Isyaana Wa'harreem Alaiyya Fihees Sakhata Wan'neerana Be'avneka Ya Geyaasal Mustagiseen.""",
  },

  {
    "title": "Dua to recite on 12th M.Ramadhan",
    "page": "att",
    "audioUrl":
    "http://docs.google.com/uc?export=open&id=1IS1FIf2nOZDx9BcVhe5HbEAx6OLWA7ZX",
    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ زَيِّنّي فيهِ بِالسِّتْرِ وَالْعَفافِ، وَاسْتُرْني فيهِ بِلِباسِ الْقُنُوعِ وَالْكَفافِ، وَاحْمِلْني فيهِ عَلَى الْعَدْلِ والإنصاف، وَآمِنّي فيهِ مِنْ كُلِّ ما أخاف، بِعِصْمَتِكَ يا عِصْمَةَ الْخائِفينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Aaraasta Kar Mujko Is Mahineme Pardaa'daari Aur Paarsaai Ke Saath, Aur Chhupa Mujko Isme Qnaa'at (Santosh) Aur Kefaayat Sha'aari (Karkasar) Ke Libaas Me Aur Aamaada Kar Mujko Isme Adaalat Aur Insaaf Par Aur Baa'amn (Be Khouf) Karaar De Mujko Isme Har Oos Cheezse Jisse Mai Darta Hu Aur Khouf Karta Hu. Apni Hidaayat Se Ay Hifaazat Karnewaalo Ki.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Decorate me in it with a covering and with honors, shield me in it with the outfit of contentment and sufficiency, enable me in it to be just and fair, and bring me in it security against what I fear with Your protection, O Protector of the fearful!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahumma Zay'yeen'nee Fihe Bis'sitre Wal Afaafe Wastoorni Fihe Be Lebaaseel Konoo'a Wal Kafaafe Wah'meelni Fihe Alal Adle Wal Insaafe Wa Aameenni Fihe Minkulle Maa Akhaafo Be Ismateka Ya Ismatal Kha'afeen.""",
  },

  {
    "title": "Dua to recite on 13th M.Ramadhan",
    "page": "att",
    "audioUrl":
    "http://docs.google.com/uc?export=open&id=14ZDtCdUPJRA2FqFrbSYhPcdb9LgiPVGk",
    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ طَهِّرْني فيهِ مِنَ الدَّنَسِ والأقذار، وَصَبِّرْني فيهِ عَلى كائِناتِ الأقدار، وَوَفِّقْني فيهِ لِلتُّقى وَصُحْبَةِ الأبرار، بِعَوْنِكَ يا قُرَّةَ عَيْنِ الْمَساكينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Paak Kar Mojko Is Mahineme Kasaafat Aur Najaasato Se Aur Motaham'meel (Sahan Karnewala) Bana Mujko Qazaa Wa Kadarke Hawaadees Par Aur Taufeek De Mujko Isme Parhezgaari Aur Achchhe Logoki Sohbatki Apni Imdaadse. Ay Gareebo Ki Aakho Ki Thandak.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Purify me in it from uncleanness and filth, enable me in it to be patient about whatever the fates bring, grant me success in it for righteousness and for the company of the kind ones with Your assistance, O apple of the eyes of the indigent!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahumma Tah'heerni Fihe Menad'danse Wal Akzaare Wasab'beerni Fihe Alaa Qaaenateel Akdaare Wa Waf'feekni Fihe Lit'toka Wa Sohbateel Abraare Be Awneka Ya Kurrat Ayneel Masaakeen.""",
  },

  {
    "title": "Dua to recite on 14th M.Ramadhan",
    "page": "att",
    "audioUrl":
    "http://docs.google.com/uc?export=open&id=1rVdg8mCC4_XXmMJkZNXdC8AMOITj9w5o",
    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ لا تُؤاخِذْني فيهِ بِالْعَثَراتِ، وَاَقِلْني فيهِ مِنَ الْخَطايا وَالْهَفَواتِ ، وَلا تَجْعَلْني فيهِ غَرَضاً لِلْبَلايا والآفات، بِعِزَّتِكَ يا عِزَّ الْمُسْلِمينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Na Giraft Kar Is Mahineme Meri Lagzisho Ki Aur Maaf Kar Mujko Isme Khataao Aur Galteeyo Se Aur Na Karaar De Mujko Isme Balaao Aur Aafatoka Nishaana. Apni Izzatke Waastese Ay Izzat Musalmaano Ki.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Do not penalize me in it when I slip, protect me in it from sinning and slipping, and do not be an object to trials and tribulations with Your Dignity, O One Who safeguards the dignity of the Muslims!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahumma La Toaakheezni Fihe Beel Asaraate Wa'akeelni Fihe Menal Khataaya Wal Hafawaate Walaa Tajalnee Fihe Garazal Leel Balaaya Wal Aafaate Be Izzateka Ya Izzal Muslemeen.""",
  },

  {
