    "page": "att",
    "audioUrl":
    "http://docs.google.com/uc?export=open&id=1Ulbme6IgFp3HDnNdjYkaVBavXb1k1Gy2",
    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ ارْزُقْني فيهِ طاعَةَ الْخاشِعينَ، وَاشْرَحْ فيهِ صَدْري بإنابة الْمخْبِتينَ، بأمانك يا أمان الْخائِفينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English
Khudaawanda ! Ataakar Mujko Is Mahineme Tujse Darnewaalo Ki Itaa'at Ka Darja. Aur Kushaada Kar Isme Mere Sineko Teri Taraf Lav Lagaane Waalo Ke Saath. Apni Amaan Ke Saath. Ay Khauf Zada Logoki Amaan.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Grant me in it the obedience of the devout, expand my chest in it with the return to You of those who abandoned You, through Your security, O One Who brings security to the fearful!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahummar Zukni Fihe Taa'atal Khaashe'eena Washrah Fihe Sadri Be Anaabateel Mukhbeteena Be Amaaneka Ya Ammanal Khaa'afeen.""",
  },

  {
    "title": "Dua to recite on 16th M.Ramadhan",
