    "arabic":
    """اَللّـهُمَّ اهْدِني فيهِ لِصالِحِ الإعمال، وَاقْضِ لي فيهِ الْحَوائِجَ والآمال، يا مَنْ لا يَحْتاجُ اِلَى التَّفْسيرِ وَالسُّؤالِ، يا عالِماً بِما في صُدُورِ الْعالَمينَ، صَلِّ عَلى مُحَمَّد وَآلِهِ الطّاهِرينَ
_____________________
Dua in Roman English    
Khudaawanda ! Hidaayat Kar Mujko Is Mahine me Achchhe Aa'amaal Ki Aur Puri Kar Isme Meri Haajate Aur Oommide, Ay Wo Ke Jo Mohtaaj Nahi Hai Tashreeh Aur Daryaaft (Mangna) Ka. Ay Dil ki Baato Ke Jaan'ne Waale Tamaam Aalam Ke.""",
    "translation":
    """Lord! Grant me in it guidance to do good deeds, allot for me in it the fulfillment of needs and of aspirations, O One Who needs no explanation or queries, the One Who knows the innermost of the worlds, bless Muhammed and his pure Progeny!""",
    "transliteration":
    """Allahummah Deni Fihe Lesaaleheel Aa'amaale Waqzeli Fiheel Hawaa'aja Wal Aamaal, Ya Manla Yahtaajo Alat Tafseere Was Soaale Ya Aalemam Bema Fi Sodureel Aalameen Salle Ala Mohammadiw Wa Aalehit Taahereen.""",
  },

