    "transliteration": """Sahifae Kaamelaa, Dua No.68
Bismillah Hir Rahman Nir Rahim
Khudaa Ke Naam Se Shuru Kartaa Hu Jo Panaah Chaahne Waalo Ki Panaahgaah Aur Bachaav Chaahne Waalo Kaa Wird Hai, Aur Mai Zaalimo Ki Sakhti, Hasad Karne Waalo Ke Makr Aur Sitamgaaro Ke Sitam Se Khudaa Ki Panaah Letaa Hu, Aur Mai Hamd Karne Waalo Se Badhkar Uski Hamd Kartaa Hu.

Khudaayaa ! Tu Wo Waahedo Yaktaa Hai Jiskaa Koi Shareek Nahi, Aur Wo Baadshaah Hai Jiskaa Koi Hissedaar Nahi, Tere Hukm Me Badlaav Nahi, Aur Teri Saltanat Me Ikhtelaaf Nahi, Mai Tujse Sawaal Kartaa Hu Ke Apne Khaas Bande Aur Apne Rasool H. MOHAMMAD MUSTUFAA (s.a.w.w) Par Rehmat Naazeel Farmaa.

Muje Apni Ne'amato Ke Shukr Adaa Karne Ki Is Tarah Taufeeq De Ke Jisse Teri Razaa Ki Intehaai Manzilo Ko Haasil Kar Saku, Aur Muje Apni Farmaa-Bardaari Karne, Ibaadat Ko Zaruri Samajne Aur Apne Fazlo Karam Se Apne Ajro Sawaab Kaa Haqdaar Banne Me Meri Madad Farmaa Taake Mai Teri Naa-farmaanyo Se Bach Saku, Jab Tak Zindaa Rahu, Aur Muje Uski Taufeeq De Jo Mere Liye Mufeed Hai Jab Tak Baaki Hu, Apni Kitaab Ke Zariye Meraa Sinaa Kushaadaa Karde, Aur Uski Tilaawat Ke Zariye Mere Gunaah Kam Karde, Meri Jaan Aur Mere Din Me Salaamati Ataa Farmaa, Aur Insaano Ko Mujse Khauf Me Mubtelaa Naa Kar, Aur Meri Baaki Zindagi Me Mujpar Ahsaan Farmaayaa Hai Ay Sabse Zyaadaa Rahem Karne Waale.""",
