ALHAMDO LILLAAHE MIN AWWALID DUNYAA,

ELAA FANAA-EHAA WA MENAL AAKHERATE,

ELAA BAKAAA-EHAA, ALHAMDO LILLAAHE,

A'LAA KULLE NE'MATIN, WA ASTAGHFERUL-LAAHA, 

MIN KULLE ZAMBIN WA ATOOBO ELAYHE YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.""",
